
- Requirements:

  - A C++ compiler with C++11 support.
    The following compiler has been tested:
    - GCC 4.8.2 (GNU/Linux x86_64).

  - Qt (tested with version 4.8.5).

  - libsndfile (tested with version 1.0.25).

  - PortAudio with C++ binding (tested with version v19_20140130).

  - Gnuspeech-SA (tested with version 0.1.0).

- Generate the Makefile:

  qmake
  # or
  qmake "INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr"

- Build:

  make

  # Optional (GNU/Linux):
  make install
  # or
  make install INSTALL_ROOT=/tmp/install
